dcterms:title: Bidirectional Diabolical Combination Lock

dcterms:description: A continuous control task where the agent must learn to drive a car up a hill, receiving a large reward only when it reaches the top, while incurring penalties for actions taken.
dcterms:title: MountainCarContinuous-v0
